      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流系统的流程图，从库存检查开始。起点是Logistics_StockLevel，用来判断仓库是否有货。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
