      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，StockLevel节点之后应该连接到仓库节点吧？我理解为先检查库存，然后进入Logistics_Warehouse环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，然后仓库需要调度车队，这里要做一个分支判断，用Logistics_FleetManagement来决定是否有可用车辆。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了从仓库到车队管理的连线，FleetManagement做成菱形判断节点。现在分Yes和No两条分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Yes",
        "No"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Yes分支表示有车，需要重新确认库存状态，所以回到Logistics_StockLevel；No分支表示无车，留在Logistics_FleetManagement继续等待调度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Yes",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "No",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加两条分支。确认一下：Yes走D节点到StockLevel，No走E节点留在FleetManagement，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Yes",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "No",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认。StockLevel确认后有货的话，进入物流追踪环节，生成Logistics_TrackingNumber。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，从D节点连到F节点TrackingNumber。接下来TrackingNumber需要处理什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
