      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "E节点的FleetManagement也要最终汇合到J节点，因为无论哪条路径最后都要确认追踪号。然后J再到K节点，K也是TrackingNumber，作为流程终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
