      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，E、I、H都指向J，J再到K。让我检查一下连线...等等，我发现刚才G节点直接标了Valid和Invalid，但G本身是TrackingNumber，这样标注方式对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
