      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，G是处理节点，从它引出两条带标签的边，分别标Yes和No...不对，应该是Valid和Invalid，我刚才说的是Valid和Invalid。",
      "elements_involved": [
